## Program 3: Educational Institution Employee Database

```java
// Staff.java - Root class
public class Staff {
    
    private int    code;
    private String name;
    
    // Default constructor
    public Staff() {
        this.code = 0;
        this.name = "N/A";
    }
    
    // Parameterized constructor
    public Staff(int code, String name) {
        this.code = (code > 0) ? code : 0;
        this.name = name;
    }
    
    // Getters
    public int    getCode() { return code; }
    public String getName() { return name; }
    
    // Setters
    public void setCode(int code) { this.code = (code > 0) ? code : 0; }
    public void setName(String name) { this.name = name; }
    
    // Display method
    public void displayInfo() {
        System.out.println("  Staff Code : " + code);
        System.out.println("  Name       : " + name);
    }
}
```

